Or the view from skyscraper and view from the students

102
00:08:53,180 --> 00:08:59,550
who gathered in underground plaza.

103
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:05,510
So Shinjuku, there occurred a kind of clash

104
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:09,890
between these two different gazes.

105
00:09:09,890 --> 00:09:16,740
But there are other kinds of structure of viewing and gazing in postwar Tokyo.

106
00:09:16,740 --> 00:09:22,820
I also discussed about the visuality, or viewing relationship

107
00:09:22,820 --> 00:09:25,590
around Douglas MacArthur.

108
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:30,390
And also I also discussed about the visual relationship

109
00:09:30,390 --> 00:09:34,570
around the royal family.

110
00:09:34,570 --> 00:09:40,520
In case of emperor, I several times discussed

111
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:44,250
about the relationship between people and emperor.

112
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:48,800
Before modern times, roughly speaking, the gaze from the people

113
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:52,700
could not reach to the emperor, but Meiji Government

114
00:09:52,700 --> 00:09:55,940
tried to construct the direct visualizing

115
00:09:55,940 --> 00:10:00,730
relationship between emperor and the people in this nation.

116
00:10:00,730 --> 00:10:06,890
But after the occupation the U.S. Army brought the camera

117
00:10:06,890 --> 00:10:12,170
or, visualizing machine in this society.

118
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:17,020
And image of visualizing can be duplicated

119
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:24,100
or reproduced massively through television and magazine after the war.

120
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:28,180
So these kinds of the visualizing relationship

121
00:10:28,180 --> 00:10:34,850
multiplied, or expanded and reproduced, in large scale

122
00:10:34,850 --> 00:10:41,490
and consumed after the 1960s and 1970s.

123
00:10:41,490 --> 00:10:45,300
Television camera was quite important.

124
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:48,080
In case of Tokyo Olympic Game, Tokyo Olympic Games

125
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:52,370
were visualized by television camera and consumed.

126
00:10:52,370 --> 00:10:58,100
More and more television camera, or gaze by television

127
00:10:58,100 --> 00:11:01,910
saturated throughout this society.

128
